gantt
    title Precious Metals DALP Launch Path
    dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat  %b %d

    section Foundation
    Scope programme & issuer setup     :a1, 2026-04-01, 10d
    Define asset & servicing rules     :a2, after a1, 10d

    section Build
    Configure DALP templates           :b1, after a2, 14d
    Integrate custody / settlement     :b2, after a2, 18d
    Configure compliance modules       :b3, after b1, 10d

    section Readiness
    UAT with operations                :c1, after b2, 10d
    Controls & sign-off                :c2, after c1, 5d

    section Launch
    Pilot issuance                     :d1, after c2, 5d
    Production rollout                 :d2, after d1, 5d
